'''Autocausative''' [[reflexive verb|reflexive]] signifies that the (usually animated) "referent represented by the subject combines the activity of actor and undergoes a change of state like a patient/subject".<ref name="Parry1998">{{cite journal|last1=Parry|first1=Mair|title=The reinterpretation of the reflexive in Piedmontese: 'impersonal' SE constructions|journal=Transactions of the Philological Society|volume=96|issue=1|year=1998|pages=63–116|issn=0079-1636|doi=10.1111/1467-968X.00024}}</ref>
